snippet: Wearing a leather jacket, slim-fit pants and combat boots, Qais Munhazim, 29, said he paid attention to the cut of his clothes.
abstract: Qais Munhazim, photographed in Uptown section of Minneapolis, endeavors to show different side to his home country of Afghanistan with his fashionable clothes.
lead_paragraph: Wearing a leather jacket, slim-fit pants and combat boots, Qais Munhazim, 29, said he paid attention to the cut of his clothes.
